ActBretton Woods and Related Agreements Act
PrecisAppointment of LESLIE MACLEAN, Deputy Minister for International Development, Department of Foreign Affairs, Trade and Development, to be Alternate Governor of the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development, and as Alternate Governor of the Multilateral Investment Guarantee Agency, to hold office during pleasure, in the place of Diane Jacovella.
